'''Edward Risk Allah''' (born 21 August 1913) was an Egyptian [[basketball]] player. He competed in the men's tournament at the [[1936 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ri/edward-risk-allah-1.html |title=Edward Risk Allah Olympic Results |accessdate=10 June 2018}}</ref>

